      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "Well-kept older car in good overall condition and a solid example for someone wanting a clean, enjoyable driver. It presents nicely inside and out, with good paint, trim, glass, and interior condition, and it appears to have been maintained and cared for over time. This is not a concours or fully restored car, but it is far better than an average driver, with only the sort of minor age-related wear and imperfections you would expect from a used vehicle. A buyer can expect a handsome, usable car that shows well, feels complete and honest, and should be enjoyable to own and drive as-is.",
